org.md2k.datakitapi.messagehandler

Class MessageType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.md2k.datakitapi.messagehandler.MessageType

  • public class MessageType
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines integer value constants used to denote message types.

    Message types are:

    • CONNECT
    • DISCONNECT
    • REGISTER
    • UNREGISTER
    • SUBSCRIBE
    • INSERT
    • QUERY
    • FIND
    • SUBSCRIBED_DATA
    • INTERNAL_ERROR
    • QUERYPRIMARYKEY
    • INSERT_HIGH_FREQUENCY
    • QUERYSIZE
    • SUMMARY
